snippet.title: Amber Heard Accusing Depp Supporters are Getting Paid | Flixet
snippet.description:
In today’s video we’ll tell you everything Amber Heard has to say about Depp supporters, who according to her are getting paid. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

Amber Heard, has spoken out to denounce the allegedly “paid” social media campaign employing Twitter “bots” to “smear and harass” her with the ultimate aim of having her fired from the role of Mera in a sequel to Aquaman. 

Music In This Video : 

Track: Odessa — LiQWYD & Scandinavianz
Music provided by Audio Library Plus
Watch: https://youtu.be/jNy-Dp3lgcg
